 <h2>Index to Information about <br>
  Herbalife International </h2>
 <p><!--BEGIN ABSTRACT-->
   <A HREF="http://www.herbalife.com/">Herbalife International,</A> founded in 1980, markets dietary supplements, herbs, weight-management
products, and personal care products. </p>
 <H4>Early History</H4>
 <UL>
   <LI><A HREF="herbalife01.html">Herbalife's Early Days (1980-1986)</A> (updated 12/17/04)
   <LI><A HREF="herbalife02.html">Herbalife Criticized at Senate
     Hearings (1985) </A><A HREF="herbalife01.html">)</A> (posted
     11/12/99)
   <LI><A HREF="herbalife03.html">Herbalife Hearings, Part II (1985) </A><A HREF="herbalife01.html">)</A> (posted 11/12/99)
   
  </UL>
 <h4>Regulatory Actions   </h4>
 <UL>
   <LI class="feature2">California Attorney General Action (1985-1986)
     <ul>
